              EnumAudioSamplingFreqType UserCommonAudioUpdateUserDefineAudioGenFreq(void)
C51 COMPILER V9.60.0.0   USERCOMMONINTERFACE                                               08/27/2025 11:01:53 PAGE 114 

              {
